:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6902:\"\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/6-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"824\" data-link=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2019/05/13/wordpress-translation-day-4-in-nha-trang/attachment/6/\" class=\"wp-image-824\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/6-1024x576.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/6-300x169.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/6.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Sng ngy 11/05/2019, ti co-working space Vn Phng Chia S  De Train Nha Trang  din ra chng trnh WordPress Translation Day 4 in Nha Trang (Ngy Hi Dch Thut WordPress Ton Cu Ln 4 ti Nha Trang) do Nha Trang WordPress t chc.</p>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-816\"></span>\n\n\n\n<p>Chng trnh  nu ln tm quan trng ca vic pht trin i ng tnh nguyn vin dch thut Li WordPress, Giao Din v Plugins ra hn 186 ngn ng bn a trn ton cu l mt trong nhng yu t quan trng dn n s pht trin v ph bin ca WordPress trong hn 15 nm qua.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngoi vic hng dn mi ngi tham gia ng gp bn dch Ting Vit trn WordPress.Org, cc quy nh khi tham gia dch thut WordPress, Ban t chc cn trnh by nhiu th thut, tin ch h tr cho vic dch thut tr nn d dng v thun tin hn.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ban t chc xin trn trng cm n co-working space Vn Phng Chia S  De Train Nha Trang  h tr rt nhiu cho bui meetup, cm n metabox.io  ti tr cc phn qu hp dn cho cc thnh vin n tham d meetup.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Xin cm n v hn gp li ti chng trnh meetup Thng 6/2019 ca Nha Trang WordPress.</p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/1-1024x768-1024x768.jpg\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/1-1024x768-1024x7