("200","1","2018-09-28 14:26:37","2018-09-28 07:26:37","Ma ma, kh hu nm m khng ch lm mi trng tr nn ngt ngt kh chu m cn l tc nhn thc y s pht trin ca nm, mc nhng tc nhn gy nh hng trc tip ti sc khe con ngi.\nVi 5 nm kinh nghim lm vic trong nghnh my lc khng kh, maylockhi.co.vn xin a ra gii php cho bt tin ny\nHu ht cc my lc khng kh Sharp u c tnh nng lc sch khng kh, bi bn, khng khun... tuy nhin sn phm ngy cng c ti u ha p ng nhu cu ngy cng cao ca con ngi.\n\nTy din tch phng nh hay to s c tng Model tng ng\n\nMy lc khng kh Sharp v ht mDW-D12A cho phng din tch: 25m2\nModel Sharp DW-E16FA cho din tch phng: 38m2\nModel DW-D20A cho phng din tch: 50m2\n\nNgoi ra cn c cc dng sn phm mylc khng kh Sharp kt hp bt mui, lc khng kh kt hp to m v lc khng kh chuyn dng:\n\nModel FP-FM40Elc khng kh v bt mui cho phng rng 30m2\nMy lc khng kh v to m KC-F30EV cho phng din tch 21m2\nModel Sharp FP-F40E cho phng 30m2\nModel FP-F30E lc khng kh v ht mcho phng din tch 21m2\nMy lc khng kh Sharp FU-A80EA cho phng din tch 62m2\n\nSn phm c bit hu ch cho gia nh bn vo ma nm m, hoc nhng gia nh c tr s sinh.\nVi nhng nhu cu a dng ca khch hng, chng ti t ho mang ti dch v y ,chu o nht..... ng ngi lin h vi chng ti  c t vn:","My lc khng kh Sharp - gii php khng kh trong ma ma","","publish","open","open","","may-loc-khong-khi-sharp-giai-phap-khong-khi-xanh-trong-mua-mua","","","2018-09-28 21:42:36","2018-09-28 14:42:36","","0","https://bizhostvn.com/w/dienmay3/?p=200","0","post","","0"),
