("475","1","2018-09-28 21:37:52","2018-09-28 14:37:52","Vi kinh nghim 5 nm bn My lc khng kh ti th trng Vit Nam, chng ti <strong>maylockhi.com.vn</strong> xin php c a ra mt s kinh nghim mua my lc khng kh, hi vng y s l nhng thng tin hu ch cho cc bn.\nMy lc khng kh mi gia nhp th trng Vit Nam nn n thi im hin ti, mi ch tip cn c s lng khch hng rt t, trong khi mi trng ti Vit Nam, c bit l cc thnh ph ng dn c nh H Ni, H Ch Minh, Qung Ninh, Hi Phng....khng kh ngy cng  nhim v nhu cu ang rt cao.\nTrc ht chng ta cn hiu nguyn tc hot ng ca My lc khng kh: Cc loi my lc khng kh c cu to bi mt qut ht dng  i lu khng kh, lung khng kh  nhim b ht vo u vo i qua h thng mng lc ( t 2 n 5 mng ty hng) cc hp cht gy  nhim bao gm: bi, mi, vi khun s b gi li ni mng lc (mi mng lc c tc dng khc nhau) khng kh sch s c a ra qua ca thot, mc  sch ph thuc vo cht lng ca h thng mng lc. Ngoi ra mt s hng b sung thm h thng pht ion m, ozone, n cc tm ...  tit trng khng kh mt cch trit  hn. Sn phm khng kh cui cng l khng khi sch  (bi, mi, khun...) sn phm c bit tt cho ngi gi, tr nh v cc bnh nhn b h hp, d ng.\nVy th <strong>my lc khng kh no tt</strong>? Mi nh sn xut u mnh v 1 tnh nng v hng ti mt phn khc khch hng c th:\n<h2><strong>My lc khng kh Panasonic</strong></h2>\nL sn phm ph bin, gi cnh tranh v nhiu tnh nng u vit, l sn phm dnh cho phn khc khch hng thu nhp trung bnh, vi chi ph khong 3 triu ng l  c th s hu 1 sn phm y  tnh nng.\n\n<img src=\"http://maylockhi.com.vn/profiles/maylockhicomvn/uploads/attach/post/images/tac-dung-4-f-pxl45a.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n<h2>My lc khng kh Sharp</h2>\nL sn phm nhp khu chnh hng sn xut ti Thi Lan, sn phm c nhiu khch hng bit ti vi kh nng lc sch khng kh v bt mui. Bn cnh  my cn c tch hp tnh nng ht m, hong kh qun o, rt thch hp cho cc gia nh vo ma nm m, c bit l cc gia nh c tr nh. Ngoi ra dng my lc kh trn  t cng l li th ca Sharp vi hnh thc bt mt, thit k nh xinh v kh nng kh mi hiu qu.\n<h2>My lc khng kh Hitachi</h2>\nL dng my nhp khu chnh hng ti Nht bn, sn phm cc k hp dn i vi khch hng yu thch hng Nht Ni a cht lng cao, ngoi tnh nng u vit, sn phm cn rt bt mt, l ni tht sang trng cho cc gia nh. Sn phm c tch hp kh nng to m, rt thch hp cho thi tit hanh kh hoc phng s dng iu ha lin tc. Sn phm dnh cho cc gia nh c din tch ln, u im ln nht l tui th mng lc cao t 8-10 nm, chnh v vy tuy s tin ban u b ra ln nhng thi gian s dng di, v sinh mng lc n gin.\n<h2>My lc khng kh Coway</h2>\n<img src=\"http://maylockhi.com.vn/profiles/maylockhicomvn/uploads/attach/post/images/cong-nghe-loc-khi-sharp.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\n\nL dng sn phm cao cp sn xut ti Hn Quc, sn phm mnh v kh nng lc phn hoa, cc tc nhn gy d ng nn c bit tt vi i tng khch hng hay b d ng khi giao ma ( phn hoa, bi, khi thuc...), ngoi ra sn phm c u t v hnh thc nn s lm ni bt cho ni tht gia nh bn ( sn phm bc da  trng gng)\n<h2>My lc khng kh Daikin</h2>\nHin ti c duy nht 1 model my, nhng kh nng lc kh mnh m, my l la chn rt thch hp cho nhng phng rng b  nhim mi, cc k thch hp cho qun cafe, tim nail, salon tc, phng ht karaoke....nhng ni b m mi ha cht, thuc l.....\nMy lc khng kh Lifepro l dng sn phm mang thng hiu Vit Nam, sn phm ph bin nht l my lc khng kh trn  t, vi tnh nng ozon kh mi nhanh chng, gip cho xe khng b m mi, khng b say xe, c bit tt vi xe taxi hoc xe cng cng.....\n\nMt im ng lu  nht i vi khch hng khi chn mua my l din tch phng s dng, mi model my ch tng ng vi din tch phng nht nh. Vic p dng ng din tch khuyn co s pht huy ti a tc dng lc kh v tui th ca my.\nVi nhng nhu cu a dng ca khch hng, chng ti t ho mang ti dch v y ,chu o nht..... ng ngi lin h vi chng ti  c t vn:\n\n<strong>Cng ty TNHH TM v SX i Hi Thy</strong>\n Hotline: <strong>0907 635 222 - 0912 034 122 - 098 653 6698</strong>\n Email: thanhhaitran34@gmail.com\n Website: maylockhi.com.vn","Kinh nghim i chn mua my lc khng kh cho ngi mi tm hiu","","inherit","closed","closed","","418-revision-v1","","","2018-09-28 21:37:52","2018-09-28 14:37:52","","418","https://bizhostvn.com/w/dienmay3/tin-tuc/418-revision-v1/","0","revision","","0"),
