("736","1","2018-09-29 00:30:28","2018-09-28 17:30:28","<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>QU KHCH HNG THN MN</p>\n<p>Chnh sch bn hng ti Asano Profitness c xy dng da trn uy tn v s mnh mang n sn phm tt nht, giao dch thun tin nht cho khch hng.</p>\n<p>1. CAM KT BN HNG Asano Profitness Nhanh chng gii p cc thc mc, cung cp thng tin chnh xc v cc vn  lin quan n sn phm, n hng v ca hng.</p>\n<p>Cung cp thng tin v cc chng trnh khuyn mi khi mua online hoc mua ti ca hng mt cch r rng, m bo quyn li cho khch hng. Lun cung cp sn phm mi ng cht lng, ng nh hnh nh v thng tin ng ti. Gi b mt tuyt i thng tin ca khch hng. Khng chia s cho cc c nhn v t chc khc.</p>\n<p>2. CAM KT V HON I HNG HA iu kin: Trong vng 7 ngy k t ngy mua sn phm. Sn phm i tr l do li nh sn sut.</p>\n<p>Mi sn phm ch c i mt ln duy nht. Cn y  ha n mua hng v nhn mc. Sn phm cn nguyn tnh trng nh ban u, cha b h hng, try xc. GHI CH: Trng hp khch c nhu cu i sn phm m khng phi do li ca nh sn xut: Asano Profitness ch p dng i vi sn phm c gi bn t 35,000,000 VN v sn phm i phi c gi bn ln hn sn phm  mua.</p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->","Chnh sch bn hng","","publish","closed","closed","","chinh-sach-ban-hang-2","","","2019-04-15 19:42:48","2019-04-15 12:42:48","","0","https://bizhostvn.com/w/dienmay3/?page_id=736","0","page","","0"),
("737","1","2018-09-29 00:30:28","2018-09-28 17:30:28","Kangaroo Vit Nam giao hng ti tt c cc khu vc tnh thnh trn phm vi ton lnh th Vit Nam. Chnh sch giao hng ca Kangaroo Vit Nam c th nh sau:\n<ol>\n 	<li><b> PHM VI P DNG</b> <b>:</b></li>\n</ol>\nTt c cc khch hng mua sn phm Kangaroo ti website <b>kangaroovietnam.vn</b> c nhu cu giao hng trc tip ti nh.\n<ol start=\"2\">\n 	<li><b> HNH THC P DNG:</b></li>\n</ol>\n-  i vi khch hng  khu vc<b></b>ni thnh<b></b>\" <b>H Ni, TP H Ch Minh v Hi Phng</b> Kangaroo Vit Nam min ph vn chuyn v lp t\n\n-  Ngoi trng hp giao hng min ph trn, cc trng hp cn li s c tnh ph giao hng theo bng ph vn chuyn ca hng vn chuyn th 3 hoc theo bng ph ca Kangaroo Vit Nam. Chi ph ny s c KangarooVit Nam thng bo v xc nhn vi qu khch trc khi qu khch tin hnh thanh ton v Kangaroo Vit Nam tin hnh gi hng\n<ol start=\"3\">\n 	<li><b> THI GIAN GIAO HNG :</b></li>\n</ol>\n- Thi gian giao hng s t 1-7 ngy ty vo khong cch vn chuyn.\n\n- Trong mt s trng hp khch quan Kangaroo Vit Nam c th giao hng chm tr do nhng iu kin bt kh khng nh thi tit xu, iu kin giao thng khng thun li, xe hng hc trn ng giao hng, trc trc trong qu trnh xut hng.\n\n- Trong thi gian ch i nhn hng, Qu khch c bt c thc mc g v thng tin vn chuyn xin vui lng lin h hotline <b>1900 63 64 06</b> ca Kangaroo Vit Nam  nhn tr gip.\n<ol start=\"4\">\n 	<li><b> TRCH NHIM VI HNG HA VN CHUYN .</b></li>\n</ol>\n- Dch v vn chuyn ca Kangaroo Vit Nam do Kangaroo Vit Nam ch nh s chu trch nhim vi hng ha v cc ri ro nh mt mt hoc h hi ca hng ha trong sut qu trnh vn chuyn hng t Kangaroo Vit Nam n qu khch.\n\n- Qu khch c trch nhim kim tra hng ha khi nhn hng. Khi pht hin hng ha b h hi, try xc, b v, mp mo, hoc sai hng ha th k xc nhn tnh trng hng ha vi Nhn vin giao nhn v thng bo ngay cho B phn chm sc khch hng theo s hotline ca Kangaroo Vit Nam.\n\n- Sau khi qu khch  k nhn hng m khng ghi ch hoc c  kin v hng ha. Kangaroo Vit Nam khng c trch nhim vi nhng yu cu i tr v h hng, try xc, b v, mp mo, sai hng ha, t qu khch sau ny.\n\n- Nu dch v vn chuyn do qu khch ch nh v la chn th qu khch s chu trch nhim vi hng ha v cc ri ro nh mt mt hoc h hi ca hng ha trong sut qu trnh vn chuyn hng t Kangaroo Vit Namn qu khch. Khch hng s chu trch nhim cc ph v tn tht lin quan.\n<ol start=\"5\">\n 	<li><b> CAM KT</b></li>\n</ol>\nKangaroo Vit Nam s giao hng ti tt c cc tnh thnh trong phm vi ton quc. Vi i ng nhn vin k thut, giao hng chuyn nghip ca cng ty. Chng ti cn lin kt vi cc hng vn chuyn hng ha chuyn nghip v uy tn trn th trng nh Tn Thnh, Viettel Post.... m bo cho hng ha c m bo an ton v ng hn vi qu khch hng.\n\nMi  kin ng gp ca qu khch vui lng lin h vi chng ti qua Email: <a href=\"mailto:support@kangaroovietnam.vn\">support@kangaroovietnam.vn</a> hoc gi vo s hotline: <b>1900 63 64 06</b>\n\nRt hn hnh c phc v qu khch!","Chnh sch bn hng","","inherit","closed","closed","","736-revision-v1","","","2018-09-29 00:30:28","2018-09-28 17:30:28","","736","https://bizhostvn.com/w/dienmay3/tin-tuc/736-revision-v1/","0","revision","","0"),
