("1130","1","2019-04-15 19:40:02","2019-04-15 12:40:02","<strong>1</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>I TNG C BO HNH</strong>:\n<ul>\n 	<li>Gh massage, my tp th thao, my massage, bp t v cc sn phm khc ca thng hiu OKIA .</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>2. THI HN BO HNH  NI CHUNG</strong><strong>:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Thi gian bo hnh ca gh massage: 24 thng (hng mi) v 12 thng (hng trng by) k t ngy mua sn phm.</li>\n 	<li>Thi gian bo hnh ca my massage v thit b my tp th thao: 12 thng (hng mi) v 06 thng (hng trng by) k t ngy mua sn phm.</li>\n 	<li>Thi gian bo hnh ca bp t: 12 thng (hng mi) v 06 thng (hng trng by) k t ngy mua sn phm.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>3. CC TRNG HP SN PHM KHNG C BO HNH</strong><strong>:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Nhng sn phm Ssano Profitness ch nh khng bo hnh.</li>\n 	<li>Khch hng khng xut trnh c phiu bo hnh hoc phiu bo hnh b ty xa, sa cha ni dung trong phiu, khng c ng du, ch k ca i din bn bn hng.</li>\n 	<li>Sn phm  qu thi gian bo hnh.</li>\n 	<li>Sn phm h hng do thin tai, ha hon, chp in, chut cn, s dng sai quy cch hay qu thng s k thut cho php ca sn phm.</li>\n 	<li>Khch hng t tho lp, sa cha sn phm.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>4. NHNG B PHN SAU KHNG THUC PHM VI BO HNH:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Lp vi, da bc, nha bc ca sn phm.</li>\n 	<li>Thn v v bp.</li>\n 	<li>Lp v nha phn thnh gh, lng gh, phn bo v hp mch v phn chn gh.</li>\n 	<li>Cc ph kin i km nh pin, ming dn, dy ni (nu c). Cc i ngun (adapter) c bo hnh trong vng ba (03) thng k t ngy mua sn phm.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong>5.NHNG TRNG HP SA CHA C TNH PH THEO QUY NH CA CNG TY:</strong>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Sn phm khng c bo hnh (trong mc 3).</li>\n 	<li>Ph kin i cng sn phm.</li>\n 	<li>Nhng b phn khng thuc phm vi bo hnh.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong><em><u>* Lu :</u></em></strong>Khch hng khng xut trnh c phiu bo hnh th ton b cc ni dung bo hnh s b tnh ph khi sa cha.","Chnh sch bo hnh","","inherit","closed","closed","","817-revision-v1","","","2019-04-15 19:40:02","2019-04-15 12:40:02","","817","https://bizhostvn.com/w/dien